u%20police%20has%20filed%20counter%20FIRs%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20IT%20cell%20leader%20Amit%20Malviya%20and%20Ayodhya%20priest%20Paramhans%20Das%20on%20Wednesday%20(September%206).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDas%20was%20booked%20for%20allegedly%20issuing%20death%20threats%20to%20Udhayanidhi%20while%20Malviya%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20triggering%20tension%20and%20inciting%20violence%20against%20the%20minister.%20The%20two%20face%20charges%20under%20multiple%20sections%20of%20IPC%2C%20including%20provocation%20to%20cause%20a%20riot%2C%20promoting%20enmity%2C%20and%20criminal%20intimidation%2C%20the%3Cem%3E%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsanatan-dharma-row-tn-police-books-amit-malviya-for-distorting-udhayanidhi-stalins-speech-8927963%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsanatan-dharma-row-tn-police-books-amit-malviya-for-distorting-udhayanidhi-stalins-speech-8927963%2F%5C%22%3EFIR%20against%20Udhayanidhi%20and%20Kharge%20was%20registered%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Rampur%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%20(September%206)%20by%20one%20Ram%20Singh%20Lodhi%2C%20a%20lawyer%2C%20who%20alleged%20that%20his%20religious%20sentiments%20had%20been%20hurt%20by%20the%20statements%20made%20against%20sanatana%20dharma.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUdhayanidhi%2C%20while%20attending%20an%20event%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Ozhippu%20Maanaadu%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Sanatana%20Abolition%20Conclave%E2%80%99%5D%20organised%20by%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Progressive%20Writers%20and%20Artists%20Association%20to%20critique%20the%20concept%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%2C%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-behead-udhayanidi-stalin-myself-if-required-paramhans-das-on-sanatana-dharma-remarks%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CIf%2520required%252C%2520I%2520myself%2520will%2Con%2520Tuesday%2520(September%25205).%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20congratulate%20the%20organisers%20for%20calling%20the%20conference%20as%20%E2%80%98eradication%20of%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%98opposing%20sanatana%20dharma%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6There%20are%20certain%20things%20which%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20and%20we%20cannot%20merely%20oppose.%20Mosquitoes%2C%20dengue%2C%20corona%20and%20malaria%20are%20things%20which%20we%20cannot%20oppose%2C%20we%20have%20to%20eradicate%20them.%20Sanatanam%20is%20also%20like%20this.%20Eradication%20and%20not%20opposing%20sanatanam%20has%20to%20be%20our%20first%20task.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-behead-udhayanidi-stalin-myself-if-required-paramhans-das-on-sanatana-dharma-remarks%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CIf%2520required%252C%2520I%2520myself%2520will%2Con%2520Tuesday%2520(September%25205).%5C%22%3Estatement%20sparked%20a%20controversy%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Malviya%20interpreted%20the%20remarks%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccall%20for%20%5Bthe%5D%20genocide%E2%80%9D%20of%20sanatanis%2C%20who%20he%20claimed%20comprise%20%E2%80%9C80%25%20%5Bof%20the%5D%20population%20of%20Bharat%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECommenting%20on%20Udhayanidhi%E2%80%99s%20remarks%2C%20Kharge%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fudhayanidhi-stalin-sanatan-dharma-remark-priyank-kharge-8923776%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DAny%2520religion%2520that%2520does%2520not%2520have%2520equal%2520rights%2520and%2520does%2CVenugopal%2520fleshing%2520out%2520their%2520ideology.%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Any%20religion%20that%20does%20not%20have%20equal%20rights%20and%20does%20not%20treat%20you%20as%20a%20human%20being%20is%20as%20good%20as%20a%20disease.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20police%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwill-behead-udhayanidi-stalin-myself-if-required-paramhans-das-on-sanatana-dharma-remarks%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CIf%2520required%252C%2520I%2520myself%2520will%2Con%2520Tuesday%2520(September%25205).%5C%22%3EDas%20had%20announced%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%2010%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20anyone%20who%20could%20behead%20Udhayanidhi.%20According%20to%20the%20complainant%2C%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%E2%80%99s%20(DMK%E2%80%99s)%20Madurai%20city%20unit%20legal%20adviser%20J.%20Devasenan%2C%20the%20Ayodhya%20religious%20leader%20had%20said%20that%20if%20no%20one%20came%20forward%2C%20he%20would%20take%20on%20the%20task%20himself.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20brazen%20threat%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20release%20of%20a%20video%20where%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20minister%20was%20symbolically%20pierced%20with%20a%20sword%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsanatan-dharma-row-tn-police-books-amit-malviya-for-distorting-udhayanidhi-stalins-speech-8927963%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20said%20the%20video%20led%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwidespread%20fear%20and%20religious%20tension%E2%80%9D%20among%20people%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMalviya%20is%20said%20to%20have%20distorted%20the%20essence%20of%20(Udayanidhi%E2%80%99s)%20speech.%20Malviya%20purportedly%20suggested%20that%20the%20minister%20incited%20violence%20against%20those%20practising%20Sanatan%20Dharma%E2%80%A6.%20Udhayanidhi%20clarified%20his%20stand%2C%20stating%20he%20had%20never%20incited%20any%20form%20of%20violence%E2%80%A6that%20he%20had%20always%20stood%20up%20against%20social%20injustices%20perpetrated%20by%20certain%20elements%20within%20religious%20frameworks%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20societal%20harm%20caused%20by%20diseases%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20police%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694084122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsanatana-dharma-row-counter-firs-filed-against-bjps-amit-malviya-ayodhya-priest%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Paramhans%20Das%20was%20booked%20for%20allegedly%20issuing%20death%20threats%20to%20Udhayanidhi%20while%20Malviya%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20triggering%20tension%20and%20inciting%20violence%20against%20the%20minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsanatana-dharma-row-counter-firs-filed-against-bjps-amit-malviya-ayodhya-priest%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Buddhas%20in%20Suburbia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07162249%2FBhagwan_Shree_Rajneesh_and_disciples_in_darshan_at_Poona_in_1977.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3ELondon%20Calling%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0How%20does%20India%20look%20from%20afar%3F%20Looming%20world%20power%20or%20dysfunctional%20democracy%3F%20And%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20Britain%2C%20and%20the%20West%2C%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20know%20about%20and%20perhaps%20learn%20from%3F%20This%20fortnightly%20column%20helps%20forge%20the%20connections%20so%20essential%20in%20our%20globalising%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20allure%20of%20the%20East%20has%20always%20been%20its%20rich%20religious%20heritage.%20Spirituality%20in%20all%20its%20guises%2C%20from%20ashrams%20to%20yoga%2C%20gives%20India%20at%20least%20as%20much%20global%20street%20cred%20as%20those%20more%20widely%20touted%20cultural%20staples%2C%20curry%20and%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20one%20of%20the%20attractions%20of%20the%20West%20for%20purveyors%20of%20Eastern-style%20enlightenment%20has%20been%20the%20small%20but%20highly%20visible%20bohemian%20audience%20for%20all%20sorts%20of%20spiritual%20and%20quasi-spiritual%20esoterica.%20The%20two%20haven%E2%80%99t%20always%20combined%20happily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20seekers%20and%20the%20gurus%2C%20there%20have%20been%20quite%20a%20number%20who%20were%20either%20charlatans%20or%20easily%20seduced%20from%20their%20chosen%20path.%20But%20there%20have%20also%20been%20remarkable%20women%20and%20men%20who%20have%20willingly%20adapted%20to%20an%20entirely%20new%20spiritual%20register.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20330px)%2085vw%2C%20330px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22330%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed.jpg%20526w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2F20115409%2Funnamed-247x300.jpg%20247w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-649461%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22402%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20new%20book%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Nirvana%20Express%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Mick%20Brown%20explores%20the%20enduring%20attraction%20in%20the%20West%20of%20Eastern%20paths%20of%20enlightenment%20and%20the%20well-trodden%20route%20heading%20West%20taken%20by%20an%20assortment%20of%20holy%20men%2C%20God%20men%2C%20gurus%20and%20lamas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20engrossing%20account%20has%20twin%20starting%20points.%20One%20is%20Sir%20Edwin%20Arnold%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Light%20of%20Asia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20rendition%20of%20the%20life%20of%20the%20Buddha%20at%20an%20almost%20intimidating%20length%20(5%2C300%20lines%20of%20prose%20poetry).%20It%20was%20published%20in%201879%2C%20selling%20more%20than%20a%20million%20copies%20and%20attracting%20much%20favourable%20comment.%20In%20Brown%E2%80%99s%20judgment%2C%20the%20verse%20epic%20%E2%80%99made%20Buddhism%20fashionable%E2%80%99%20in%20London%20drawing%20rooms.%20Queen%20Victoria%20even%20lobbied%2C%20unsuccessfully%2C%20for%20Arnold%20to%20become%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20poet%20laureate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20point%20of%20embarkation%20is%20Swami%20Vivekananda%E2%80%99s%20astonishingly%20bold%20and%20successful%20appearance%20at%20a%20huge%20gathering%20in%20Chicago%20in%201893%20which%20christened%20itself%20the%20World%E2%80%99s%20Parliament%20of%20Religions.%20This%20was%20%E2%80%98a%20historic%20attempt%20to%20bring%20together%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20a%20public%20forum%20the%20spiritual%20traditions%20of%20East%20and%20West%E2%80%99.%20Christianity%E2%80%99s%20foray%20into%20India%20was%20in%20large%20part%20as%20the%20creed%20of%20the%20coloniser%3B%20Eastern%20spirituality%E2%80%99s%20venture%20in%20the%20other%20direction%20relied%20much%20more%20on%20the%20mystical%2C%20life-affirming%20message%20of%20some%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20venerated%20religious%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20315px)%2085vw%2C%20315px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07162114%2F71XHwVZtgLL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07162114%2F71XHwVZtgLL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_.jpg%20667w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07162114%2F71XHwVZtgLL._AC_UF10001000_QL80_-200x300.jpg%20200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671860%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22472%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EMick%20Brown%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Nirvana%20Express%3A%20How%20the%20Search%20for%20Enlightenment%20Went%20West%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EHurst%20Publishers%2FPenguin%20India%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Nirvana%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20snakes%20its%20way%20through%20Sri%20Aurobindo%2C%20Meher%20Baba%2C%20Maharishi%20Mahesh%20Yogi%20and%20many%20others%20right%20up%20to%20Bhagwan%20Shree%20Rajneesh%2C%20%E2%80%98the%20most%20brilliant%20and%20most%20controversial%20guru%20of%20the%20age%E2%80%99.%20It%E2%80%99s%20difficult%20to%20find%20any%20holy%20man%20who%20was%20untouched%20by%20the%20adulation%20of%20those%20desperately%20seeking%20enlightenment%2C%20or%20at%20least%20a%20quieter%20soul.%20Several%20come%20across%20as%20complete%20shysters.%20But%20amid%20their%20ranks%20were%20several%20spiritual%20teachers%20of%20profound%20wisdom%20and%20humility.%20And%20among%20the%20western%20seekers%2C%20jostling%20with%20the%20na%C3%AFve%20and%20the%20needy%2C%20were%20such%20luminous%20talents%20as%20Annie%20Besant%2C%20Aldous%20Huxley%2C%20Allen%20Ginsberg%20and%20George%20Harrison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20East%20%E2%80%93%20or%20perhaps%20a%20part-obscured%20vision%20of%20the%20Orient%20%E2%80%93%20was%20embraced%20by%20America%E2%80%99s%20Beat%20movement%2C%20shaped%20Hippy-dom%2C%20and%20lives%20on%20in%20New%20Age-influenced%20beliefs%20and%20practices.%20There%20were%20casualties%2C%20of%20course%3B%20some%20followers%20were%20exploited%2C%20financially%20and%20sexually%2C%20by%20men%20who%20pretended%20they%20were%20bestowing%20blessings.%20But%20a%20greater%20awareness%20of%20Eastern%20spiritual%20beliefs%20and%20practices%20has%20been%20of%20universal%20benefit%20and%20Brown%E2%80%99s%20story%20%E2%80%93%20well%20researched%20and%20sparklingly%20told%20%E2%80%93%20is%20uplifting%20as%20well%20as%20hugely%20entertaining.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrown%20is%20a%20onetime%20rock%20music%20journalist%20who%20has%20become%20a%20well-regarded%20author%20and%20feature%20writer.%20In%20his%20books%2C%20he%20keeps%20returning%20to%20the%20theme%20of%20Eastern%20religions%20%E2%80%93%20he%20has%20written%20about%20spiritual%20tourism%20to%20India%20and%20about%20the%20Karmapa%20Lama%20controversy%20%E2%80%93%20with%20a%20persistence%20that%20might%20suggest%20he%20has%20hopped%20on%20board%20the%20Nirvana%20Express%20himself.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20goes%20along%20every%20Sunday%20to%20his%20local%20parish%20church%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20his%20name%20seems%20familiar%2C%20well%2C%20four%20years%20ago%20he%20was%20the%20journalist%20who%20famously%20tracked%20down%20and%20filmed%20Nirav%20Modi%2C%20the%20fugitive%20billionaire%20whose%20idea%20of%20going%20incognito%20was%20to%20promenade%20down%20London%E2%80%99s%20Oxford%20Street%20in%20an%20ostrich-hide%20jacket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20curious%20silences%20in%20Brown%E2%80%99s%20account%3A%20very%20little%20about%20Islam%20in%20general%20and%20Sufism%20in%20particular%2C%20which%20for%20quite%20a%20few%20British%20spiritual%20acolytes%20was%20encountered%20as%20an%20Indian%20religious%20practice%20even%20if%20its%20roots%20were%20elsewhere%3B%20and%20a%20reluctance%20to%20explore%20the%20cross-over%2C%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20between%20pursuing%20Eastern%20religious%20beliefs%20and%20endorsing%20India%E2%80%99s%20national%20cause.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20era%20of%20unforgiving%20religious%20nationalism%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20now%20less%20opportunity%20for%20seeking%20shared%20spiritual%20space%20and%20travelling%20%E2%80%93%20literally%20and%20figuratively%20%E2%80%93%20to%20seek%2C%20or%20offer%2C%20enlightenment.%20That%20diminishes%20us%20all.%20Those%20tiny%20models%20of%20the%20Buddha%20which%20were%20once%20commonplace%20in%20British%20suburban%20parlours%20didn%E2%80%99t%20point%20to%20any%20great%20spiritual%20understanding%2C%20but%20they%20did%20express%20an%20inquisitiveness%20and%20appreciation%20for%20ideas%20rooted%