ephanie%20Chon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChon's%20father%20bought%20the%2011-acre%20property%20for%20%249.75%20million%20in%202016%2C%20and%20Stephanie%20Chon%20rents%20the%20space%20from%20C.Castle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20more%20than%20a%20year%20for%20Chon%20to%20get%20a%20special-use%20permit%20from%20the%20county%20that%20would%20allow%20her%20to%20turn%20the%20building%20into%20a%20health%20club.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Chons%20took%20on%20the%20renovation%20without%20much%20help.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221136%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20lobby%20and%20front%20desk%20post-renovation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f79295781926001911b289%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22852%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lobby%20and%20front%20desk%20post-renovation.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stephanie%20Chon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20Chons%20took%20on%20the%20renovation%20without%20the%20team%20of%20employees%20they'd%20relied%20on%20for%20other%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20used%20to%20have%20a%20team%20of%20engineers%2C%20a%20team%20of%20architects%2C%20and%20a%20team%20of%20designers%20helping%20us%20with%20every%20project%20and%20then%20COVID%20hits%2C%26quot%3B%20Chon%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20father%2C%20being%20the%20entrepreneur%20he%20is%2C%20was%20losing%20his%20mind%20being%20shut%20down.%20He%20was%20like%2C%20'You%20know%20what%2C%20I'm%20just%20gonna%20start%20demoing%20this%20building.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20idea%20was%20to%20build%20a%20wellness%20center%2C%20not%20just%20a%20spa.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22693%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20building%20before%20a%20large%20indoor%20pool%20was%20installed.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2