aving%20to%20have%20hard%20conversations%20with%20layoffs%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20the%20business%20and%20financial%20pressures.%20I%20was%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%2C%20seeking%20self-care%2C%26quot%3B%20Chon%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20world%20was%20screaming%20that%20they%20needed%20some%20sort%20of%20outlet%20and%20that%20self-care%20was%20not%20a%20luxury%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%20it%20really%20was%20a%20priority.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20renovations%20took%20longer%20and%20were%20more%20expensive%20than%20anticipated.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20private%20suite%20under%20renovation%20in%20the%20wellness%20center.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f795ad781926001911b701%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22525%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20private%20suite%20under%20renovation%20in%20the%20wellness%20center.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Stephanie%20Chon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20club%2C%20which%20opened%20last%20fall%2C%20took%20longer%20and%20was%20more%20expensive%20to%20renovate%20than%20either%20Stephanie%20Chon%20or%20her%20father%20had%20anticipated%2C%20largely%20because%20of%20COVID-related%20complications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20hard.%20It%20was%20a%20huge%20risk%20%E2%80%94%20logistics%2C%20getting%20in%20certain%20materials%2C%20the%20premiums%20that%20we%20were%20paying%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20just%20wild%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BAt%20that%20time%2C%20shipping%20costs%20and%20freight%20costs%20were%20exorbitant.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20are%20still%2050%2C000%20square%20feet%20available%20for%20renovation.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221138%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20private%20suite%20in%20the%20wellness%20center.%5C%22%20charset%3D%