p%3EAs%20office%20attendance%20and%20productivity%20tracking%20become%20increasingly%20common%2C%20more%20companies%20are%20using%20it%20to%20evaluate%2C%20discipline%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-bosses-use-employee-tracking-software-for-remote-workers-2023-8%5C%22%3Eeven%20fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20employees.%20Employees%20who%20break%20Meta's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fall-rules-of-metas-new-aggressive-strict-rto-mandate-2023-8%5C%22%3Ereturn-to-office%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20risk%20termination%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company.%20About%20three-quarters%20of%20respondents%20in%20the%20ResumeBuilder.com%20survey%20said%20they%20had%20fired%20employees%20based%20on%20findings%20from%20their%20tracking%20software.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20if%20US%20companies%20are%20truly%20concerned%20about%20maximizing%20their%20employees'%20productivity%2C%20some%20of%20them%20may%20be%20doing%20it%20all%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslack.com%2Fresources%2Fwhy-use-slack%2Fstate-of-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%20this%20year%20from%20the%20workplace-messaging%20company%20Slack%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20a%20lack%20of%20agreement%20about%20measuring%20productivity%20between%20employees%20and%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20our%20data%2C%20visibility%20and%20activity%20ranked%20at%20the%20top%20of%20leaders'%20go-to%20metrics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslack.com%2Fresources%2Fwhy-use-slack%2Fstate-of-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESlack%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20global%20survey%20results%20from%20desk%20workers%20and%20executives%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20most%20individual%20contributors%20prefer%20to%20be%20measured%20based%20on%20what%20they%20produce%2C%20through%20team%20goals%20and%20KPIs.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F2AOpu%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22How%20execs%20primarily%20measure%20productivity%20and%20how%20desk%20workers%20wish%20their%20productivity%20was%20measured%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22356%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAaron%20Terrazas%2C%20the%20chief%20economist%20at%20Glassdoor%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20there's%20a%20%26quot%3Brich%20debate%26quot%3B%20going%20on%20about%20what%20exactly%20productivity%20was%20in%20a%20remote%20setting%20compared%20with%20in%20an%20office.%20Terrazas%20said%20that%20traditionally%2C%20economists%20and%20probably%20many%20executives%20believed%20that%20this%20would%20be%20time%20spent%20in%20the%20office%2C%20visibility%2C%20and%20the%20revenue%20an%20employee%20generated%20from%20their%20hours%20working.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20economy%20is%20no%20longer%20kind%20of%20a%20manufacturing%20economy%2C%20and%20creative%20work%20is%20not%20necessarily%20sitting%20in%20front%20of%20a%20screen%2C%26quot%3B%20Terrazas%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20starting%20to%20recognize%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20workers%20who%20are%20in%20front%20of%20a%20screen%20in%20an%20office%20aren't%20necessarily%20productive%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20workers%20who%20look%20like%20they%20are%20out%20for%20a%20run%20or%20doing%20laundry%20%E2%80%94%20that%20is%20kind%20of%20ways%20to%20spark%20creative%20productivity%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobert%20C.%20Pozen%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20MIT%20Sloan%20School%20of%20Management%20who%20has%20written%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.harpercollins.com%2Fproducts%2Fextreme-productivity-robert-c-pozen%3Fvariant%3D32893857759266%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproductivity%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20notion%20of%20tracking%20hours%20is%20so%20antithetical%20to%20being%20productive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20tracking%2C%20Pozen%20said%2C%20gives%20%26quot%3Ba%20false%20sense%20of%20accountability%26quot%3B%20because%20hours%20are%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20good%20proxy%20for%20productivity.%26quot%3B%20The%20key%20to%20figuring%20out%20productivity%2C%20Pozen%20said%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bto%20figure%20out%20what%20your%20high-priority%20objectives%20are%2C%20what%20your%20success%20metrics%20are%2C%20and%20then%20to%20focus%20on%20them%20and%20not%20to%20get%20hung%20up%20by%20how%20many%20hours%20you%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20don't%20need%20to%20stop%20keeping%20tabs%20on%20attendance%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20be%20helpful%20as%20a%20productivity%20measure.%20Paul%20Rubenstein%2C%20the%20chief%20people%20officer%20for%20the%20people-analytics%20company%20Visier%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20work%20contribution%20was%20a%20good%20measure%20versus%20attendance.%20Rubenstein%20added%20that%20attendance%20was%20still%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20telling%20people%20to%20come%20to%20the%20office%20or%20back%20to%20the%20office%20without%20any%20purpose%20to%20it%20is%20silly%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubenstein%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20won't%20connect%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20tracking%20will%20become%20the%20new%20normal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20managers%20become%20more%20comfortable%20in%20managing%20a%20remote%20workforce%2C%20and%20as%20younger%20workers%20become%20managers%20and%20have%20been%20working%20more%20of%20their%20career%20remotely%2C%20software%20monitoring%20will%20hopefully%20become%20antiquated%20and%20the%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20results%20and%20not%20the%20amount%20of%20time%20worked%2C%26quot%3B%20Stacie%20Haller%2C%20the%20chief%20career%20advisor%20at%20ResumeBuilder.com%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.resumebuilder.com%2F1-in-3-remote-employers-are-watching-you-work-from-home-on-camera%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHow%20does%20your%20company%20track%20productivity%2C%20and%20how%20do%20you%20feel%20about%20it%3F%20Reach%20out%20to%20these%20reporters%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Amhoff%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emhoff%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejzinkula%40insider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20to%20share.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-jobs-work-from-home-return-to-office-productivity-tracking-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694082601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f77307781926001911913a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-jobs-work-from-home-return-to-office-productivity-tracking-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Robert%20C.%20Pozen%2C%20a%20senior%20lecturer%20at%20MIT%20Sloan%20School%20of%20Management%2C%20says%20tracking%20hours%20isn't%20the%20best%20measure%20of%20work%20productivity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula%2CMadison%20Hoff)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-jobs-work-from-home-return-to-office-productivity-tracking-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20built%20my%20dream%20job%20creating%20drone%20videos%20for%20hotels%20and%20fancy%20Airbnbs%20in%20Mexico.%20'Everyone%20wants%20drone%20footage.'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20sid