20from%20the%20universe%20to%20go%20travel%20the%20world%20and%20live%20my%20life.%20I%20actually%20cashed%20in%20everything%20to%20my%20name%2C%20my%20401K%2C%20all%20my%20stocks%2C%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20six%20years%2C%20I've%20traveled%20the%20world.%20I%20started%20traveling%20throughout%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20where%20I%20was%20able%20to%20travel%20pretty%20cheaply.%20I've%20lived%20in%20Thailand%2C%20Turkey%2C%20and%20Albania%2C%20just%20to%20name%20a%20few.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20traveling%2C%20I%20was%20taking%20videos%20everyday%20and%20loved%20using%20Instagram.%20About%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BOk%20I%20need%20to%20figure%20out%20something%20to%20sustain%20my%20living%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20got%20me%20into%20life%20coaching%20and%20social%20media%20coaching.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20moved%20to%20Puerto%20Escondido%2C%20Mexico%2C%20in%20January%202023.%20It's%20a%20little%20surf%20town%20on%20the%20Oaxacan%20coast%20and%20still%20a%20hidden%20gem%2C%20but%20it's%20growing%20in%20popularity.%20I%20was%20feeling%20a%20little%20uninspired%20by%20my%20work%20and%20I%20love%20travel%20videos.%20Making%20content%20for%20hotels%20and%20Airbnb%20just%20felt%20like%20something%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20slid%20into%20a%20hotel's%20direct%20messages%20for%20my%20first%20gig%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20two-story%20luxury%20villa%20surrounded%20by%20palm%20trees%20and%20a%20turquoise%20pool%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f8da9856f5190019fc69cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20properties%20Weiss%20photographed.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Samantha%20Weiss%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20collaboration%20I%20