rten%2C%20she%20was%20able%20to%20do%20Grade%203%20maths.%20She%20was%20making%20crafts%20and%20games%20with%20whatever%20she%20had%2C%20sometimes%20just%20out%20of%20waste%20paper%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Khurana%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkids.guinnessworldrecords.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F9%2Fworlds-youngest-videogame-developer-made-a-cool-game-for-kids-757625%5C%22%3Etold%20GWR%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20that%20she%20would%20naturally%20excel%20at%20coding%20as%20she%20had%20an%20ideal%20combination%20of%20skills.%20So%2C%20I%20got%20her%20to%20try%20a%20demo%20coding%20class%20which%20she%20loved!%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20game%20that%20Simar%20created%20was%20called%20Healthy%20Food%20Challenge.%20She%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20after%20a%20doctor%20asked%20her%20to%20stop%20eating%20junk%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20doctor%20said%20I%20have%20to%20eat%20healthy%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20make%20a%20game%20about%20healthy%20food%20and%20junk%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20GWR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimar%20wants%20to%20help%20children%20like%20her%20learn%20the%20differences%20between%20healthy%20and%20unhealthy%20food%2C%20as%20well%20as%20why%20we%20shouldn't%20eat%20too%20much%20junk%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20loves%20mathematics%20and%20coding%20and%20want%20to%20be%20a%20game%20developer%20after%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimar%20said%20she%20is%20very%20happy%20with%20the%20Guinness%20World%20Record%20and%20didn't%20say%20no%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20attempting%20more%20records%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694081340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fjkusgm2o_simar-khurana-youngest-coder-1200_625x300_07_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fmeet-6-year-old-simar-khurana-worlds-youngest-videogame-developer-4368097%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Simar%20Khurana