Fpublications%2Fcrypto-wealth-report%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECrypto%20Wealth%20Report%202023.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Nearly%20half%20of%20this%20crowd%20%E2%80%94%2040%2C500%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20own%20Bitcoin%2C%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20at%20least%20182%20of%20crypto%20users%20have%20holdings%20of%20%24100%20million%20or%20more%20in%20cryptocurrencies%2C%20and%2022%20users%20own%20at%20least%20%241%20billion%20worth%20of%20cryptocurrencies%20each%2C%20according%20to%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%2C%20which%20worked%20with%20South%20African%20wealth%20intelligence%20firm%20New%20World%20Wealth%20to%20collect%20its%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2088%2C200-strong%20crypto-millionaire%20crowd%20makes%20up%20only%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20the%20world's%20total%20number%20of%20millionaires%2C%20of%20which%20there%20are%20more%20than%2020%20million%2C%20Andrew%20Amoils%2C%20head%20of%20research%20at%20New%20World%20Wealth%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20world's%20wealthy%20crypto%20users%20are%20starting%20to%20outnumber%20the%20number%20of%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20in%20entire%20countries%2C%20such%20as%20Russia%2C%C2%A0which%20has%2065%2C000%20millionaires%2C%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20which%20has%2052%2C000%20millionaires%2C%20per%20Amoils'%20estimate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20crypto-millionaires%20came%20into%20money%20because%20of%20their%20crypto%20investments%2C%20Dominic%20Volek%2C%20Group%20Head%20of%20Private%20Clients%20at%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%2C%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20that%20would%20be%20new%20money%20that's%20sort%20of%20adopted%20in%20the%20last%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Volek%2C%20though%20he%20added%20that%20cryptocurrency%20is%20becoming%20more%20popular%20among%20his%20firm's%20overall%20clientele.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20amateur%20investors%20also%20grew%20their%20money%20in%20cryptocurrencies%20because%20access%20to%20digital%20assets%20has%20improved%20through%20new%20apps%20and%20exchanges%2C%20Volek%20added.%20The%20crypto%20exchange%20Binance%2C%20for%20example%2C%20said%20in%20August%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.binance.com%2Fen%2Ffeed%2Fpost%2F905671%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehas%20over%20150%20million%20users%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20despite%20facing%20regulatory%20restrictions%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFive%20years%20ago%2C%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20invest%20in%20cryptocurrency%2C%20it%20was%20too%20scary.%20You%20need%20wallets%20and%20vaults%20and%20different%20exchanges%2C%20and%20which%20one%20do%20I%20use%3F%26quot%3B%20Volek%20said.%20%26quot%3BNowadays%2C%20things%20have%20gotten%20a%20lot%20more%20controlled%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20lot%20safer%20to%20invest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Volek%20said%20his%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20which%20offers%20migration%20services%20to%20the%20wealthy%20%E2%80%94%20has%20seen%20some%20crypto-millionaire%20clients%20lose%20much%20of%20their%20wealth%20amid%20a%20volatile%20digital%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20recalled%20several%20young%20men%20who%20attained%20%2420%20million%20or%20so%20from%20trading%20crypto%2C%20but%20could%20no%20longer%20continue%20with%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners'%20programs%20after%20the%20March%202022%20Bitcoin%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20affect%20them%20so%20much%20that%20they%20would%20say%3A%20'Hang%20on%2C'%20or%20they%20would%20withdraw%20from%20applying%20because%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20they%20didn't%20have%20that%20liquidity%20anymore%2C%20or%20weren't%20comfortable%20with%20participating%20in%20one%20of%20these%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcryptocurrency-millionaires-new-wealth-digital-currency-henley-partners-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22publis