0-traffic-curbs-now-hours-away-delhi-preps-for-arrival-of-world-leaders-4367122%5C%22%3EG20%20Summit%20begins%20in%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20security%20has%20been%20tightened%20around%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20a%20controlled%20zone%20will%20be%20created%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district%20for%20the%20weekend%20conclave.%C2%A0Apart%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-blog-g20-summit-pm-modi-on-what-india-aims-to-achieve-with-grand-show-at-g20-summit-4367402%5C%22%3EG20%20meet%3C%2Fa%3E%20venue%20-%20Bharat%20Mandapam%20in%20Pragati%20Maidan%20-%20global%20leaders%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20stay%20in%20hotels%20in%20the%20district%20and%20visit%20important%20historical%20buildings%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20their%20security%20and%20smooth%20movement%2C%20special%20restrictions%20have%20been%20put%20into%20place%20for%20people%20and%20vehicles%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area.%20Apart%20from%20Pragati%20Maidan%2C%20areas%20of%20Lutyen's%20Delhi%20which%20house%20stately%20bungalows%2C%20luxury%20hotels%20and%20government%20buildings%20will%20be%20under%20the%20controlled%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhole%20Delhi%20is%20open.%20Restrictions%20are%20only%20imposed%20in%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20NDMC%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%20said.%20Here's%20what%20the%20weekend%20will%20look%20like%20for%20you%2C%20if%20you%20live%20in%20the%20area%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20will%20the%20restrictions%20last%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20Delhi%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20overall%20movement%20of%20vehicles%20will%20be%20difficult%20with%20restrictions%20imposed%20from%20midnight%20tonight%20to%20September%2010%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20New%20Delhi%20residents%20be%20allowed%20to%20travel%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20living%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%20will%20be%20allowed%20entry%20and%20exit%2C%20but%20those%20coming%20from%20outside%20will%20need%20special%20passes%2C%20as%20per%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20three-seater%20rickshaws%20(TSRs)%20and%20taxis%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20or%20run%20in%20the%20area%20from%205am%20on%20Saturday%20to%2011.59pm%20on%20Sunday.%C2%A0Goods%20vehicles%2C%20commercial%20vehicles%2C%20interstate%20buses%2C%20and%20local%20city%20buses%2C%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20operate%20on%20Mathura%20Road%20(beyond%20Ashram%20Chowk)%2C%20Bhairon%20Road%2C%20Purana%20Quila%20Road%2C%20and%20inside%20Pragati%20Maidan%20Tunnel%20from%20midnight%20on%20September%207%20until%2011.59%20PM%20on%20September%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20taxis%20carrying%20bonafide%20residents%20and%20tourists%20having%20valid%20bookings%20in%20hotels%20located%20inside%20New%20Delhi%20district%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20and%20move%20within%20the%20district.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20advised%20that%20residents%20and%20essential%20service%20providers%20moving%20within%20the%20area%20carry%20identity%20proof%20documents.%C2%A0City%20buses%20will%20not%20be%20available%20in%20the%20New%20Delhi%20area%20but%20buses%20will%20operate%20on%20Ring%20Road%20and%20road%20network%20beyond%20Ring%20Road%20towards%20the%20borders%20of%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20visit%20theatres%2C%20malls%20or%20restaurants%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20offices%2C%20theatres%2C%20restaurants%20and%20malls%20will%20be%20closed%20in%20New%20Delhi%20from%20September%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20all%20medical%20shops%2C%20grocery%20shops%2C%20milk%20booths%2C%20vegetable%2Ffruit%20shops%20and%20ATMs%20will%20remain%20open%20throughout%20Delhi%20including%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Police%20has%20declared%20Dhaula%20Kuan%2C%20Khan%20Market%2C%20Janpath%20and%20Bhikaji%20Cama%20Place%20as%20%26quot%3Bsensitive%20areas%26quot%3B.%20Movement%20in%20markets%20