E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20Union%20of%20States%E2%80%99%20federalist%20basic%20structure%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694069909000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F06%2F09152402%2FFUzRhJzUsAEEqu7.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchief-election-commissioner-one-nation-one-election%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rajiv%20Kumar%20has%20said%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20a%20mandate%20to%20conduct%20polls%20according%20to%20legal%20provisions.%20'And%20we%20are%20ready.'%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fchief-election-commissioner-one-nation-one-election%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Just%20In%3A%20Snack%20Brand%20Haldiram's%20Denies%20Reports%20About%20Buyout%20By%20Tata%20Group%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20report%20by%20Reuters%20dated%20September%206%20claimed%20that%20popular%20snack%20brand%20Haldiram's%20was%20apparently%20in%20talks%20with%20investors%20to%20sell%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20company.%20Tata%20Group's%20consumer%20unit%20was%20said%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20interested%20parties%20seeking%20to%20buy%20about%2051%25%20stake%20in%20the%20company%2C%20which%20Haldiram's%20valued%20at%20%2410%20billion.%20However%2C%20a%20new%20statement%20by%20Haldiram's%20has%20refuted%20the%20claims%20of%20the%20takeover%20made%20by%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffood.ndtv.com%2Fnews%2Fratan-tata-celebrates-air-india-win-with-adorable-flight-shaped-cookies-2574055%5C%22%3ERatan%20Tata%20Celebrates%20Air%20India%20Win%20With%20Adorable%20Flight-Shaped%20Cookies%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22gd6l71r%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fgd6l71r