20touched%20new%20heights.%20It%20may%20just%20be%20that%20the%20competitive%20parents%20of%20Indian%20origin%20children%20set%20even%20loftier%20goals%20for%20their%20children.%20Interestingly%2C%20all%20three%20Indian-origin%20candidates%20are%20from%20the%20Republican%20party%2C%20each%20positioning%20themselves%20as%20the%20most%20American%2C%20most%20Republican%20candidate%20of%20their%20time.%20Hirsh%20Vardhan%20Singh%20even%20refers%20to%20himself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpureblood%20candidate%26quot%3B%20for%20not%20allowing%20himself%20to%20have%20been%20vaccinated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Nikki%20Haley%20is%20known%20as%20a%20veteran%20politician%20by%20this%20time%2C%20an%20anti-establishment%20voice%20that%20has%20broken%20through%20has%20been%20that%20of%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy.%20An%20author%20and%20entrepreneur%20with%20the%20right%20Ivy%20League%20credentials%2C%20his%20policy%20ideals%20often%20read%20like%20that%20of%20amateur%20Indian%20Twitterati.%20Much%20like%20the%20Indian%20commentariat%2C%20his%20talks%20are%20replete%20with%20references%20to%20the%20American%20Deep%20State%2C%20to%20dismantling%20the%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20of%20China%20as%20enemy%20Number%20One%2C%20and%20of%20being%20proudly%20Hindu.%20The%20similarity%20may%20well%20be%20because%20the%20average%20English-educated%20Indian%20is%20much%20better%20versed%20with%2C%20and%20interested%20in%20global%20affairs%2C%20but%20his%20views%20have%20caused%20consternation%20even%20in%20his%20own%20party.%20While%20he%20has%20taken%20on%20Ron%20DeSantis%20from%20the%20right%2C%20he%20has%20refused%2C%20at%20any%20time%2C%20to%20criticize%20Donald%20Trump.%20A%20strategic%20move%20that%20allows%20him%20to%20vie%20for%20the%20Vice%20Presidency%20under%20an%20unlikely%20Trump%20Presidency%2C%20it%20also%20comes%20across%20as%20more%20sincere%20due%20to%20its%20consistency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%20has%20so%20far%20provided%20a%20unique%20outlook%2C%20one%20that%20has%20offered%20proactive%20solutions%20to%20major%20American%20and%20global%20crises.%20A%20rare%20policy-oriented%20voice%20in%20today's%20American%20politics%2C%20which%20has%20been%20heavily%20rhetorical%2C%20he%20is%20well-versed%20with%20the%20US%20Constitution%20and%20uses%20it%20to%20good%20effect.%20His%20belief%20in%20American%20exceptionalism%20as%20what%20allows%20him%20to%20compete%20for%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20his%20nation%20despite%20being%20born%20to%20immigrant%20parents%20seems%20to%20have%20helped%2C%20not%20hindered%20his%20progress%20so%20far.%20According%20to%20polls%2C%20he%20has%20climbed%20from%204%25%20polling%20average%20in%20July%20to%2010%25%20only%20a%20couple%20months%20later.%20A%20significant%20shift%2C%20his%20rise%20has%20caused%20discomfort%20in%20Republican%20ranks%20with%20undisguised%20racist%20attacks%20from%20pastors%20and%20authors%20alike%2C%20that%20has%20arguably%20only%20brought%20more%20notice%20to%20his%20campaign.%20Ramaswamy%20being%20openly%20Hindu%20has%20not%20stopped%20him%20from%20citing%20Christian%20scripture%20very%20comfortably%20to%20make%20his%20point%20on%20digital%20media%20with%20very%20wide%20reach%2C%20thus%20catering%20to%20a%20slice%20of%20the%20Republican%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%20has%20been%20relentlessly%20articulating%20his%20views%20confidently%20on%20mainstream%20as%20well%20as%20new%20age%20media.%20He%20is%20only%20the%20second%20person%20in%20the%20race%20for%20American%20Presidency%20to%20advocate%20for%20non-interventionist%20foreign%20policy%20aside%20from%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%2C%20coincidentally%20another%20Hindu%20candidate%2C%20but%20from%20the%20Left%20(formerly%20Democrat).%20His%20geopolitics%20offers%20an%20unapologetic%20withdrawal%20from%20Ukraine%2C%20mending%20fences%20with%20Russia%20and%20redrawing%20global%20borders%20to%20arrive%20at%20peace%20in%20order%20to%20break%20apart%20the%20ever-closer%20Russia-China%20embrace%2C%20and%20preventing%20Taiwan%20from%20Chinese%20attacks.%20All%20of%20this%20is%20underlined%20by%20a%20fiercely%20nationalist%20strategy%20stance%20that%20benefits%20the%20American%20people%20foremost%2C%20without%20reneging%20on%20the%20current%20American%20God-complex%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ethat%20allows%20its%20hegemony.%20For%20example%2C%20while%20Ramaswamy%20has%20sworn%20to%20protect%20Taiwan%20militarily%2C%20it%20is%20only%20to%20be%20until%20the%20time%20that%20the%20US%20achieves%20semi-conductor%20independence.%20He%20hopes%20that%20after%20that%2C%20the%20Chinese%20lose%20motive%20to%20attack%20Taiwan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20clear-eyed%20approach%20is%2C%20understandably%2C%20met%20with%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20scepticism%2C%20citing%20impossible%20idealism%20and%20lack%20of%20experience.%20Considering%20that%20Chinese%20belligerence%20is%20revanchist%20in%20nature%2C%20their%20interest%20in%20Taiwan%20is%20unlikely%20to%20recede%20once%20it%20loses%20its%20status%20as%20the%20foremost%20manufacturer%20of%20semiconductors.%20From%20an%20American%20nationalist%20perspective%2C%20though%2C%20the%20utility%20of%20military%20support%20to%20a%20faraway%20Asian%20country%20can%20cease%20at%20that%20point.%20This%20flies%20face-first%20against%20a%20%26quot%3Bvalues%20first%26quot%3B%20geopolitical%20approach%20that%20has%20been%20selectively%20employed%2C%20but%20nonetheless%20binds%20American%20strategists%20across%20the%20board.%20It%20is%20similar%20to%20his%20stance%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20calling%20Ukranian%20President%20Zelensky%20a%20fraud%2C%20and%20a%20call%20for%20an%20end%20to%20the%20ongoing%20war%20even%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20accommodating%20Russia.%20A%20red%20line%20in%20an%20establishment%20too%20used%20to%20a%20single%20big%2C%20bad%20Bond%20villain%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20Russia%2C%20the%20call%20is%20nonetheless%20justified%20from%20a%20citizen%20point%20of%20view%20that%20has%20seen%20billions%20in%20taxpayer%20money%20disappearing%20into%20corrupt%20coffers%20of%20Ukrainian%20bureaucrats.%20Bolstered%20by%20reductive%20reasoning%20with%20mass%20appeal%2C%20like%20calls%20to%20%26quot%3BSupport%20the%20Little%20Guy%26quot%3B%20and%20flags%20on%20bios%2C%20rhetoric%20around%20the%20subject%20has%20overpowered%20views%20like%20Ramaswamy's%20in%20recent%20times%2C%20but%20his%20appeals%20are%20resonating%20with%20at%20least%20some%20Republicans.%20He%20has%20been%20unabashed%20about%20calling%20Israel%20a%20staunch%20friend%2C%20and%20cites%20his%20appreciation%20for%20democracies%20like%20Israel%20and%20India%20despite%20their%20flaws%20since%20there%20are%20ideals%20such%20nations%20aspire%20to%2C%20much%20like%20the%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20domestic%20standpoint%2C%20his%20policy%20statements%20involve%20restructuring%20of%20the%20FBI%20so%20that%20redundant%20departments%20can%20be%20lopped%20off%20to%20work%20for%20the%20Drug%20Enforcement%20Authority%20(DEA)%20or%20the%20US%20Marshals.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20has%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20American%20education%20system%20that%20has%20cultivated%20culture%20wars%20and%20cancel%20culture.%20He%20advocates%20abolition%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%2C%20a%20wild%20idea%20that%20also%20finds%20appeal%20in%20a%20population%20that%20has%20moved%20to%20homeschooling%20at%20scale%2C%20especially%20post-pandemic.%20Further%20appealing%20to%20his%20right%20wing%20base%2C%20he%20has%20promised%20to%20pardon%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20all%20charges%20he%20is%20currently%20being%20held%20on%2C%20on%20technical%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20statements%20and%20internet%20popularity%20have%20garnered%20enough%20traction%20for%20him%20to%20be%20deliberately%20misquoted%20by%20far-left%20media%20such%20as%20the%20CNN%2C%20the%20Atlantic%20and%20for%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20to%20write%20an%20article%20calling%20him%20annoying.%20While%20his%20chances%20of%20winning%20the%202024%20presidency%20are%20seen%20as%20very%20low%2C%20his%20surging%20popularity%20and%20calls%20to%20move%20beyond%20identity%20politics%20seem%20to%20be%20finding%20ground.%20His%20calls%20for%20a%20revival%20of%20American%20exceptionalism%20and%20national%20pride%2C%20without%20the%20associated%20tags%20of%20white%20supremacy%2C%20have%20marked%20him%20as%20the%20wildcard%20candidate%20on%20the%20right%2C%20much%20like%20Robert%20Kennedy%20is%20seen%20as%20on%20the%20left%20of%20American%20politics.%20A%20self-made%20millionaire%2C%20his%20political%20gambit%20may%20be%20a%20personal%20dare%2C%20but%20has%20broken%20ground%20in%20mainstreaming%20conversations%20that%20were%20formerly%20restricted%20to%20Redditt%20threads%2C%20while%20embodying%20all%20the%20ideals%20of%20faith%20and%20family%20his%20party%20claims%20to%20stand%20for.%20Anti-establishment%20personalities%20have%20little%20chance%20of%20breaking%20through%20on%20any%20side%20in%20American%20politics%2C%20but%20fortune%20favours%20the%20brave%2C%20or%20so%20Ramaswamy%20seems%20to%20believe%2C%20especially%20with%20Trump%20having%20shown%20the%20way%20in%202016.%20Therein%20lies%20the%20rub%2C%20then%20-%20does%20blaspheming%20coalesce%20a%20growingly%20nervous%20population%20to%20repeat%20its%20choices%2C%20or%20does%20it%20win%20elections%3F%20The%20American%20people%20will%20decide%20soon%2C%20while%20the%20internet%20keeps%20its%20eye%20on%20the%20dark%20horse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Sagorika%20Sinha%20is%20a%20columnist%20and%20podcaster%20with%20experience%20in%20foreign%20policy%20analysis%20and%20international%20relations.%20She%20also%20writes%20about%20domestic%20policy%20when%20not%20working%20on%20her%20fledgling%20YouTube%20channel)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694068500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fnjc36av_vivek-ramaswamy-afp_625x300_31_August_23.