nurture%20our%20planet.%20As%20One%20Family%2C%20we%20support%20each%20other%20in%20the%20pursuit%20of%20growth.%20And%20we%20move%20together%20towards%20a%20shared%20future%20-%20One%20Future%20-%20which%20is%20an%20undeniable%20truth%20in%20these%20interconnected%20times%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20pulled%20out%20all%20the%20stops%20for%20the%20G20%20Summit%20where%20world%20leaders%20will%20hold%20discussions%20on%20geopolitical%20tensions%2C%20economic%20slowdowns%2C%20and%20rising%20food%20and%20energy%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20guest%20list%20includes%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20UK%20PM%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20Canada%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20and%20several%20other%20world%20leaders.%20This%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20India%20is%20hosting%20such%20a%20powerful%20group%20of%20leaders%20from%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20said%20that%20this%20is%20not%20just%20a%20high-level%20diplomatic%20endeavour%20for%20India%2C%20but%20a%20way%20to%20showcase%20the%20country's%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20India%2C%20the%20G20%20Presidency%20is%20not%20merely%20a%20high-level%20diplomatic%20endeavour.%20As%20the%20Mother%20of%20Democracy%20and%20a%20model%20of%20diversity%2C%20we%20opened%20the%20doors%20of%20this%20experience%20to%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20accomplishing%20things%20at%20scale%20is%20a%20quality%20that%20is%20associated%20with%20India.%20The%20G20%20Presidency%20is%20no%20exception.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20people-driven%20movement.%20Over%20200%20meetings%20will%20have%20been%20organised%20in%2060%20Indian%20cities%20across%20the%20length%20and%20breadth%20of%20our%20nation%2C%20hosting%20nearly%20100%2C000%20delegates%20from%20125%20countries%20by%20the%20end%20of%20our%20term.%20No%20Presidency%20has%20ever%20encompassed%20such%20a%20vast%20and%20diverse%20geographical%20expanse%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%