raw%20cash%20from%20an%20ATM%20using%20UPI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20Ravisutanjani%2C%20who%20originally%20posted%20the%20video%2C%20first%20clicks%20on%20the%20UPI%20cardless%20cash%20option%20displayed%20on%20the%20screen%20and%20is%20prompted%20to%20enter%20the%20desired%20withdrawal%20amount.%C2%A0Once%20the%20amount%20is%20entered%2C%20a%20QR%20code%20appears%20on%20the%20ATM%20screen.%C2%A0He%20then%20scans%20the%20QR%20code%20using%20the%20BHIM%20app%20and%20enters%20his%20UPI%20PIN.%20He%20collects%20the%20cash%20shortly%20after.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20the%20video%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%20wrote%2C%20''UPI%20ATM%3A%20The%20future%20of%20fintech%20is%20here!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUPI%20ATM%3A%20The%20future%20of%20fintech%20is%20here!%20%F0%9F%92%AA%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fel9ioH3PNP%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fel9ioH3PNP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Piyush%20Goyal%20(%40PiyushGoyal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPiyushGoyal%2Fstatus%2F1699652077679767851%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ESeptember%207%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unique%20ATM%20has%20been%20developed%20by%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20and%20powered%20by%20NCR%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20UPI%20ATM%20will%20act%20as%20just%20a%20regular%20ATM%2C%20and%20charges%20may%20be%20applied%20beyond%20the%20allowed%20free%20usage%20limit.%20The%20new%20UPI%20ATM%20is%20currently%20supported%20on%20the%20BHIM%20UPI%20app%2C%20but%20it%20will%20soon%20be%20live%20on%20other%20apps%20like%20Google%20Pay%2C%20PhonePe%2C%20and%20Paytm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20technology%20is%20not%20publicly%20deployed%20yet%20but%20is%20being%20rolled%20out%20in%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20innovation%2C%20one%20user%20wrote%2C%20''An%20entirely%20new%2C%20but%20a%20much-needed%20innovation!%20This%20would%20be%20especially%20beneficial%20for%20those%20who%20know%20how%20to%20use%20UPI%2C%20but%20not%20a%20debit%20card%20(there%20are%20tons%20of%20people%2C%20esp%20in%20the%20rural%20areas).%20UPI%20ATM%20would%20make%20cash%20withdrawals%20much%20easier.%20Really%20amazed%20at%20how%20far%20we've%20come%20in%20financial%20technologies.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''Great%20innovation%2C%20no%20need%20to%20carry%20physical%20cards.%20I%20am%20sure%20they%20will%20add%20in%20existing%20ATM%20machines%20too.''%20A%20third%20called%20it%20a%20''game-changer.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20UPI%20achieved%20a%20remarkable%20milestone%20by%20crossing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fupi-transactions-cross-10-billion-mark-in-august-here-s-how-it-plans-to-go-global-4347391%5C%22%3E10%20billion%20transactions%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20total%20number%20of%20UPI%20transactions%20reached%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%2010.58%20billion%20in%20August.%20A%20top%20official%20from%20the%20National%20Payments%20Corporation%20of%20India%20said%20that%20the%20country%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20do%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-has-potential-to-do-100-billion-upi-transactions-a-month-npci-ceo-4361163%5C%22%3E100%20billion%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%3C%2Fa%3E%20(UPI)%20transactions%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdl%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdl%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694064660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F56geviu_indias-first-upi-atm_625x300_07_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgame-changer-video-shows-man-withdrawing-cash-from-an-atm-using-upi-4367024%22%2C%22summary%2