network%20had%20remained%20impenetrable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20nature%20of%20widespread%20attention%20on%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20financial%20dealing%20evoked%20global%20interest%20since%20the%20expose%20done%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2Fadani-group-vs-hindenburg-research-key-developments-2328244-2023-01-30%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EHindenburg%20Report%20accusing%20the%20Adani%20Enterprises%20of%20stock%20manipulation%20and%20more%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20While%20the%20mainstream%20media%20has%20remained%20largely%20silent%20on%20the%20allegations%20on%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20manipulative%20dealings%20and%20off-shore%20operations%2C%20The%20oligarchic%20rise%20of%20the%20firm-and%20its%20network%20across%20sectors%20in%20India%20and%20outside%2C%20provides%20a%20telling%20tale%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98volatile%E2%80%99%20state%20of%20the%20relationship%20between%20big%20private%20capital%20and%20the%20Modi%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERoughly%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20this%20author%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fvoices%2Fopinion%2Fpaytm-crash-crypto-indian-markets-wild-west-phase-can-backfire%23read-more%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eexplained%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20how%20India%E2%80%99s%20stock%20market%20performance%2C%20at%20a%20macro-level%2C%20was%20witnessing%20signs%20of%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fvoices%2Fopinion%2Fpaytm-crash-crypto-indian-markets-wild-west-phase-can-backfire%23read-more%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewild%20west%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20phenomenon%20with%20a%20range%20of%20IPOs%20or%20initial%20public%20offerings%20(from%20Paytm%20to%20Zomato)%20in%20the%20fintech%20space%20busting%20flat.%20Profits%20were%20soaring%20high%20for%20a%20few%20firms%20while%20others%2C%20despite%20low%20earning%2C%20were%20aiming%20big%20in%20raising%20cash%20through%20IPO%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlying%20these%20volatile%2C%20bullish%20stock%20trends%20shaping%20a%20K-shaped%20economic%20recovery%20for%20the%20economy%20lies%20deep-rooted%20structural%20concern%20that%20many%20observing%20the%20economy%20miss%3A%20the%20widening%20discord%20between%20the%20stock%20market%20performance%20of%20listed%20firms%20(or%20those%20new%20to%20raising%20capital)%20and%20the%20underlying%20macro-numbers%20of%20their%20actual%20performance%2C%20P-E%20ratio%2C%20debt%20positions%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20crisis%20terminology%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20growing%20disconnect%20between%20the%20performance%20of%20capital%20markets%20and%20the%20real%20economy%20also%20signals%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20bubble%2C%20or%20a%20mania.%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Emania%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eproblem%20may%20accentuate%20in%20the%20future%20if%20similar%20such%20episodes%20(what%20was%20seen%20in%20the%20Paytm-Zomato%20instance%20or%20the%20Hindenburg-Adani%20face-off)%20continue%20causing%20massive%20selloffs%20in%20temporal%20intervals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%2C%20in%20explaining%20the%20Indian%20stock%20market%20performance%20behaviour%20over%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20the%20substantive%20rise%20in%20price-driven%20expectations%20or%20stock%20prices%20cannot%20be%20explained%20by%20any%20logical%20deduction%2C%20or%20an%20objective%20faith%20in%20the%20evident%20performance%20of%20market%20fundamentals%2C%20or%20by%20the%20strength%20of%20an%20economy%E2%80%99s%20K-shaped%20recovery.%20Rather%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20explained%20by%20the%20irrational%20exuberance%20visible%20among%20investors%20amid%20short-term%20capital%20inflows%20driven%20from%20foreign%20institutional%20investors%20(FIIs)%2C%20most%20of%20which%20has%20been%20%E2%80%98hot%20money%E2%80%99%2C%20apart%20from%20those%20invested%20in%20form%20of%20equity-backed%20systematic%20investment%20plans%20(SIPs).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20own%20rise%20is%20built-in%20or%20embedded%20in%20this%20pattern%20of%20financial%20capitalism%20for%20India.%20A%20question%20pertinent%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20observers%20has%20been%3A%20How%20long%20a%20wild%20west%20mentality%20would%20continue%20to%20grip%20investor%20sentiment%20in%20stocks%20(or%20in%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20poster%20boy%20image)%20is%20difficult%20to%20estimate-one%20can%E2%80%99t%20predict%20how%20investors%20would%20react%20to%20rhetoric%20or%20narrative-fuelled%20speculative%20information%20flows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENevertheless%2C%20what%20is%20certain%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20underlying%20performance%20of%20the%20equity%20market%20may%20continue%20seeing%20periodic%20peaks%20and%20troughs%20spaced%20between%20short-timed%20intervals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%2C%20therefore%2C%20raises%20a%20series%20of%20fundamental%20political%20economy%20questions%20for%20a%20fragile%2C%20disorganised%2C%20asymmetric%20biz-financial%20landscape%20like%20India%E2%80%99s%2C%20where%20the%20concentration%20of%20wealth%20and%20profit-generating%20power%20is%20vested%20in%20less%20than%20top%201%25%20of%20the%20oligarchic%20capitalist%20class%2C%20mostly%20run%20as%20family%20based%20conglomerates%2C%20while%20the%20others%20(99%25)%20suffer%20with%20high%20prices%2C%20stagnating%20wages%2C%20poor%20employment%20growth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20vital%20political%20economy%20questions%20on%20the%20state-private%20capital%20relationship%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENoted%20political%20economist%20Atul%20Kohli%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fpanorama%2Feconomic-reforms-the-widening-gulf-between-hope-and-reality-1014040.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20his%20work%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20politics%20of%20economic%20growth%20in%20India%20(1980-2005%20period)%2C%20provided%20a%20detailed%20insight%20into%20the%20%E2%80%98political%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98political%20economy%E2%80%99%20landscapes%20shaping%20India%E2%80%99s%20growth%20trajectory%20during%20the%201980s%2C%201990s%2C%20and%202000s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20work%20highlights%20the%20essence%20of%20seeing%20India%E2%80%99s%20entry%20to%20the%20global%20economic%20landscape%20(in%20the%2090s)%20as%20a%20product%20of%20incremental%2C%20gradualist%20reforms%20of%20the%2080s%20based%20on%20attitudinal%20shifts%20observed%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98state-capital-private%20business%E2%80%99%20relationship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20central%20to%20the%20pursuit%20of%20Kohli%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fpanorama%2Feconomic-reforms-the-widening-gulf-between-hope-and-reality-1014040.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethesis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20theoretical%20(more%20abstract)%20question%3A%20Did%20India%E2%80%99s%20growth%20acceleration%20(during%20the%201990s%2C%202000s)%20resulted%20from%20the%20(nation)%20state%E2%80%99s%20embrace%20of%20neoliberal%20(or%20pro-market)%20policies%2C%20or%20from%20some%20more%C2%A0complex%C2%A0but%20identifiable%20pattern%20of%20state%20intervention%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%201991%20and%20post-1991%20period%20is%20understood%20as%20part%20of%20the%20pro-market%20growth%20trajectory%20where%20pursued%20economic%20reforms-undertaken%20more%20on%20the%20capital%20market%20side-allowed%20our%20%E2%80%98markets%E2%80%99%20to%20operate%20more%20freely%2C%20flexibly%20in%20certain%20sectors%20(telecom%2C%20automobiles%2C%20aviation%2C%20IT%2C%20construction%2C%20consumer%20goods%20etc.)%20with%20the%20aim%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ecrowd%20in%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20private%20investment%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20a%20push%20for%20market-led%20growth%20allowed%20economic%20possibilities%20and%20upward%20income%20mobility%20for%20higher%20income%20classes%20across%20the%20nation%2C%20even%20though%20the%20distributive%20end%20of%20any%20such%20growth-accrued%20gains%20failed%20to%20allow%20greater%20income%20(and%20social%20mobility)%20amongst%20the%20more%20vulnerable%2C%20economically%20depressed%20classes.%20Welfare%20distribution%20or%20essential%20social%20expenditure%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20prioritised%20in%20fiscal%20policy%20for%20most%20of%20the%2090s%20and%20thereon.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENevertheless%2C%20from%20this%20period%20onwards%2C%20one%20saw%20a%20strengthening%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98state-capital-private%20business%E2%80%99%20alliance%20like%20never%20before%2C%20often%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20preexisting%20social%20and%20economic%20protection%20available%20to%20India%E2%80%99s%20deeply%20fragmented%20labor%20force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani-Modi%20alliance%20based%20on%20a%20newly%20designed%20%E2%80%98pro-business%E2%80%99%20regulatory%20outlook%20emerging%20from%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rise%20to%20power%20at%20the%20national%20level%20post%202014%20signals%20a%20similar%20phase%20in%20theory%2C%20but%20with%20a%20new%20twis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Adam%20Tooze%20argued%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fadamtooze.substack.com%2Fp%2Fchartbook-190-the-adani-crisis-is%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ein%20a%20column%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EDriving%20national%20infrastructure%20development%20(in%20India)%2C%20Adani%20personifies%20the%20oligarchic%20linkages%20and%20rentier%20profits%20generated%20by%20licensing%20system%20for%20infrastructure%20on%20which%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20growth%20model%20has%20heavily%20relied.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20lot%20written%20and%20said%20about%20the%20success%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Fvoices%2Fopinion%2Fgujarat-polls-pm-modis-high-growth-weak-development-paradox-vs-aaps-welfarism-prime-minister-narendra-modi-gujarat-model%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Gujarat%20growth%20model%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20pivoted%20around%20the%20emergence%20and%20wider%20presence%20of%20such%20network%20linkages%20and%20rentier%20profits%2C%20driven%20by%20large%20capital%20infra-investment%20from%20firms%20like%20Adani%E2%80%99s%2C%20which%2C%20ever%20since%20Modi%20became%20PM%2C%20entered%20the%20national%20scene.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20growth%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20a%20cycle%20between%20rising%20equity%20values%20and%20corporate%20debt.%20Already%20In%202014%20Gautam%20Adani%20boasted%20that%20his%20deals%20were%20%E2%80%9Cimmensely%20bankable%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F474706d6-1243-4f1e-b365-891d4c5d528b%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EFT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Enoted%20back%20in%202020%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20argue%20the%20concentration%20of%20economic%20power%20in%20family-run%20conglomerates%20is%20a%20way%20to%20fast-track%20India%E2%80%99s%20economic%20development%2C%20like%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Echaebol%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0did%20for%C2%A0post-war%C2%A0South%20Korea.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fwhy-the-modi-government-policy-of-national-champions-is-unravelling%5C%22%3EWhy%20the%20Modi%20Government%20Policy%20of%20%E2%80%98National%20Champions%E2%80%99%20Is%20Unravelling%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20true%20that%20family-run%20businesses%20have%20been%20important%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20business%20historical%20landscape%20always%2C%20but%20never%20before%20have%20any%20one%20or%20two%20large%20conglomerates%2C%20holding%20large%20assets%2C%20been%20this%20debt-exposed%20the%20corporate%20sphere%20to%20borrowings%20from%20state-run%20banks%2C%20public%20exchequer%20money%20at%20this%20level.%20It%20signals%20the%20realisation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98too%20big%20to%20fail%20syndrome%E2%80%99%20for%20certain%20institutions%2C%20which%20will%20make%20foreign%20investors%20more%20wary%20from%20investing%20in%20India%20(FDI%20levels%20as%20a%20result%20have%20already%20been%20quite%20volatile).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20New%20India%E2%80%99s%20state-big%20business%20compact%2C%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20big%20capital%20firms%20like%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20are%20exposed%20to%20national%20asset%20classes%2C%20financed%2Fdepended%20on%20the%20exchequer%20(or%20citizen%20tax%20money)%20requires%20greater%20scrutiny.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EState-owned%20banks%20have%20already%20lent%20twice%20as%20much%20to%20the%20Adani%20group%20as%20private%20banks%2C%20with%2040%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20lending%20being%20done%20by%20SBI.%20This%20irresponsibility%20has%20exposed%20the%20crores%20of%20Indians%20who%20have%20poured%20their%20savings%20into%20LIC%20and%20SBI%20to%20financial%20risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20summate%2C%20a%20short%20reflection%20on%20the%20probable%20trajectory%20state%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20political%20economy%20state%2C%20amidst%20all%20this%20news%20is%20deeply%20warranted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fopinion%2Fpanorama%2Funder-modi-india-is-following-1980s-latam-778188.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecolumn%20written%20few%20years%20ago%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20this%20author%20also%20argued%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20growth%20trajectory%20and%20state-private%20capital%20relationship%20was%20reflecting%20common%20traits%20with%201980s%20Latin%20America%20and%20the%20Russia%20of%201990s%2C%20amidst%20a%20rise%20in%20crony%20like%20oligarchic%20capitalism%2C%20where%20an%20ad-hoc%20%E2%80%98pro-business%E2%80%99%20policy%20outlook%20was%20making%20certain%20firms%20to%20monopolise%20asset%20ownership%2C%20rent-extraction%20at%20the%20top%20level%20(with%20support%20of%20the%20government)%2C%20while%20cutting%20down%20on%20competition%20and%20the%20entry%20of%20new%20firms%2C%20across%20sectors.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20meteoric%20rise%20in%20the%20India%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20governance%20space%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20umbrella%20support%20%E2%80%93%20much%20like%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20part%20of%20shaping%20that%20oligarchic%20trajectory%2C%20which%20is%20worrisome%20for%20the%20ills%20of%20monopolistic%20influence%20on%20in-equalising%20India%E2%80%99s%20already%20divided%20K-shaped%20growth%20pattern.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issues%2C%20raised%20here%2C%20strike%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20India%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20sector%2C%20its%20financial-capital%20scene%2C%20where%20a%20select-few%20family-controlled%20conglomerates%20dominate%20the%20business%20scene%20in%20an%20opaque%20manner%2C%20exposing%20the%20faultlines%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20governance%20system%20and%20the%20shallow-functioning%20of%20a%20weak%2C%20anti-competitive%20regulatory%20structure.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeepanshu%20Mohan%20is%20Professor%20of%20Economics%20and%20Director%2C%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%2C%20O.P.%20Jindal%20Global%20University.%20He%20is%20a%20Visiting%20Professor%20to%20the%20School%20of%20International%20Development%20and%20Global%20Studies%2C%20University%20of%20Ottawa%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20an%20Honorary%20Research%20Fellow%2C%20Birkbeck%20College%2C%20University%20of%20London%20this%20Fall.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EA%20version%20of%20this%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694063565000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2FModi-Adani-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fmodi-adani-oligarchy-stock-offshore%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20India%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20sector%2C%20a%20select-few%20family-controlled%20conglomerates%20dominate%20the%20business%20scene%20in%20an%20opaque%20manner%2C%20exposing%20the%20faultlines%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20corporate%20governance%20system.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fmodi-adani-oligarchy-stock-offshore%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India's%20G20%20presidency%20giving%20voice%20to%20many%20nations%3A%20Mahindra%20Gr%20CEO%20Shah%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694062447000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-09%2F07%2Ffull%2F1694062306-1125.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-s-inclusive-g20-presidency-giving-voice-to-many-countries-mahindra-gr-md-ceo-anish-shah-123090700169_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20further%20said%2C%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20more%20important%20is%20that%20India%20is%20uniquely%20positioned%20for%20bridging%20the%20divide%20between%20many%20countries%20in%20the%20world%2C%20in%20some%20cases%20a%20North-South%20divide%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engageme