a%3E.%20I%20think%20everybody%20is%20coming%20with%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20seriousness%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fno-delhi-declaration-west-g20-sherpas%5C%22%3ENo%20Delhi%20Declaration%3F%20West%20Rejects%20India%E2%80%99s%20Compromise%20Text%20at%20G20%20Sherpas%20Meeting%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAsked%20whether%20Moscow%20and%20Beijing%20were%20%E2%80%9Cmiffed%E2%80%9D%20with%20India%2C%20Jaishankar%20denied%20it.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20no.%20I%20do%20not%20think%20it%20has%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20India.%20I%20think%20whatever%20decision%20they%20make%E2%80%A6I%20mean%20they%20would%20know%20best.%20But%20I%20would%20not%20at%20all%20see%20it%20the%20way%20you%20would%20suggest%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20minister%20also%20reiterated%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%E2%80%99%20absence%20will%20have%20any%20impact%20on%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20G20%20summit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20put%20it%20this%20way%2C%20the%20issues%20are%20there%20these%20are%20not%20issues%20that%20are%20this%20morning%20being%20taken%20up.%20I%20mean%20there%20is%20a%20whole%20gestation%20period%20of%20eight-nine%20months%2C%20where%20at%20different%20levels%20ministers%20or%20officials%20have%20tried%20to%20progress%20an%20issue.%20So%2C%20this%20is%20like%20a%20culmination%20you%20know%2C%20that%20is%20what%20this%20is%20really%20about.%20There%20are%20really%20about%2016-18%20processes%20which%20are%20all%20coming%20together%20to%20be%20stitched%20up%20together%20to%20produce%20a%20summit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20reiterated%20that%20the%20efforts%20to%20get%20a%20consensus%20on%20a%20final%20declaration%20is%20still%20on.%20%E2%80%9CWell%2C%20we%20are%20negotiating%20right%20now%20as%20I%20said%20the%20negotiation%20is%20not%E2%80%A6%20The%20clock%20did%20not%20start%20ticking%20yesterday%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20G20%20sherpas%20are%20still%20discussing%20the%20text%20of%20the%20declaration%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20sign%20of%20compromise%20from%20either%20the%20West%20or%20Russia%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20issue.%20While%20both%20sides%20had%20agreed%20on%20a%20negotiated%20text%20at%20Bali%20last%20year%2C%20Russia%20and%20China%20had%20withdrawn%20their%20support%20soon%20after.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20joint%20statements%20have%20been%20issued%20after%20any%20of%20the%20G20%20ministerial%20meetings%20held%20so%20far%20under%20the%20Indian%20presidency.%20Instead%2C%20India%20has%20been%20issuing%20a%20document%20termed%20as%20%E2%80%9Cchair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20and%20outcome%20document%E2%80%9D%20to%20reflect%20that%20Russia%20and%20China%20do%20not%20want%20the%20G-20%20grouping%20to%20talk%20about%20Ukraine%20or%20other%20geo-political%20conflicts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Jake%20Sullivan%20also%20indicated%20that%20it%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20release%20a%20Delhi%20declaration%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20summit%20on%20Sunday.%20%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20to%20get%20absolute%20consensus%20on%20a%20statement%20on%20Ukraine%20is%20challenging%20because%20you%E2%80%99ve%20got%20Russia%20seated%20at%20the%20table%2C%20albeit%20not%20at%20the%20leader%20level%20because%20Putin%20isn%E2%80%99t%20going%20to%20be%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fpress-briefings%2F2023%2F09%2F05%2Fpress-briefing-by-press-secretary-karine-jean-pierre-and-national-security-advisor-jake-sullivan-6%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehe%20told%20reporters%20at%20a%20White%20House%20briefing%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22p