redibility%2C%2520traction%2C%2520and%2520representativeness.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ESenegalese%20President%20Macky%20Sall%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20his%20chairmanship%20of%20the%20AU%20in%202022%2C%20urging%20G20%20leaders%20to%20grant%20the%20African%20bloc%20a%20permanent%20seat%20within%20the%20group.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CRussia%20believes%20that%20once%20implemented%2C%20the%20initiative%20of%20African%20nations%20would%20contribute%20to%20strengthening%20the%20positions%20of%20the%20majority%20of%20countries%20worldwide%20and%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20Global%20South%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lukash%20told%20the%20Russian%20media%20outlet.%20She%20also%20reminded%20that%20Russia%20had%20recently%20held%20a%20Russia-Africa%20summit%20in%20St%20Petersburg%20in%20July%2C%20where%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20had%20publicly%20voiced%20his%20support%20for%20the%20AU%20joining%20G20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERussia%20had%20been%20wooing%20African%20countries%20and%20the%20Global%20South%20aggressively%2C%20as%20many%20of%20them%20had%20a%20more%20ambiguous%20position%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20and%20had%20abstained%20on%20UN%20resolutions%20related%20to%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20Russia%20and%20China%2C%20EU%20was%20stepping%20up%20its%20outreach%20to%20African%20countries%20on%20the%20sideline%20of%20the%20G20%20summit.%20Terming%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98mini%20summit%E2%80%99%2C%20top%20EU%20leadership%20and%20national%20leaders%20like%20German%20chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20will%20hold%20a%20meeting%20on%20September%209%20with%20their%20counterpart%20from%20South%20Africa%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Nigeria%20and%20current%20AU%20chair%2C%20Comoros.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20gathering%20of%20EU%20and%20African%20leaders%20on%20F