0are%20well-supported.%20It%20is%20more%20Russia%20that%20is%20isolated%20than%20G7%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20official%20noted%20that%20Ukraine%20will%20certainly%20dominate%20the%20discourse%20at%20the%20summit%2C%20since%20it%20would%20be%20on%20%E2%80%9Ceverybody%E2%80%99s%20mind%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20an%20illusion%20that%20you%20will%20just%20address%20economic%20topics.%20Of%20course%2C%20maybe%20you%20can%20say%20this%20for%20finance%20ministers%20and%20ministers%20and%20you%20have%20all%20those%20discussions.%20But%20when%20you%20have%20leaders%2C%20then%20it%20becomes%20more%20geopolitical.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20maybe%20the%20only%20forum%20where%20you%20have%20this%20plenary%20seating%20of%20leaders%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%2C%20friction%20is%20also%20expected%20on%20the%20issues%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20multilateral%20development%20banks%20and%20debt%20management.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20EU%20official%20mentioned%20that%20Russia%20and%20China%20have%20reservations%20about%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20Bali%20declaration%20from%20last%20year%2C%20particularly%20regarding%20its%20language%20regarding%20the%20reduction%20of%20fossil%20fuel%20use%20and%20emissions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1694024174000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F04141303%2FFjHNMmeakAEkbxa.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Feu-official-says-indian-text-on-ukraine-does-not-go-far-enough%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20senior%20official%20noted%20that%20Ukraine%20will%20certainly%20dominate%20discourse%20at%20the%20G20%20summit%20this%20year%2C%20adding%20that%20when%20leaders%20are%20involved%2C%20talks%20become%20more%20geopolitical.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3