20Maanoj%20points%20out%2C%20the%20idea%20for%20Mission%20ICU%20was%20in%20no%20way%20a%20happy%20accident%2C%20but%20rather%2C%20very%20intentional.%20Maanoj%20has%20a%20number%20of%20social%20impact%20projects%20to%20his%20name%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20of%20which%20is%20%E2%80%98Corona%20Champions%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20its%20purpose%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20COVID%20started%20reaching%20rural%20areas%2C%20the%20people%20who%20contracted%20the%20virus%20in%20these%20places%20were%20treated%20like%20untouchables.%20Through%20this%20initiative%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20tell%20stories%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327807%2Fgautam-yadav-person-living-with-hiv-shares-myths-and-things-to-know%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal-life%20champions%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20fought%20the%20pandemic%20head-on.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaanoj%20was%20joined%20by%20Dr%20Ashwin%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Vaatsalya%20chain%20of%20hospitals%20%E2%80%94%20a%20network%20attempting%20to%20provide%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20semi-urban%20and%20rural%20areas%20with%20affordable%20healthcare%20facilities.%20The%20duo%20spent%20a%20major%20part%20of%20the%20first%20wave%20of%20the%20lockdown%20chronicling%20these%20stories%20and%20compiled%20them%20into%20a%20short%20film%20that%20won%20people%E2%80%99s%20hearts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%2C%20when%20the%20second%20COVID%20wave%20hit%2C%20we%20were%20wondering%20what%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20Maanoj%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20around%20this%20time%20that%20another%20public%20health%20expert%20Dr%20Edmond%20Fernandes%20crossed%20paths%20with%20Maanoj.%20Dr%20Edmond%20leads%20a%20number%20of%20projects%20in%20Mangaluru%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325599%2Fmadurai-jiovio-healthcare-startup-pregnancy-risk-mon