cal%20experience%20before%20joining%20a%20course.%20He%20got%20a%20job%20in%202017%20at%20Hostellers%2C%20a%20backpackers%20hostel%20chain%2C%20in%20his%20city%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%2C%20he%20says%2C%20changed%20his%20life%20for%20good.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20the%20biggest%20turning%20point%20in%20my%20life.%20Watching%20other%20travellers%20made%20me%20understand%20how%20travelling%20could%20be%20fun.%20I%20used%20to%20be%20a%20fool%20dreaming%20about%20making%20movies%20about%20other%20countries%20while%20our%20India%20was%20exploding%20with%20culture.%20I%20was%20convinced%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20as%20much%20time%20as%20I%20could%20travelling%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20expressed%20to%20my%20father%20that%20I%20wanted%20to%20travel%20the%20country.%20He%20told%20me%20that%20if%20travelling%20is%20what%20makes%20me%20happy%2C%20I%20should%20leave%20my%20job%20and%20do%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20enough%20motivation%20for%20me%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20this%20idea.%20My%20father%20also%20offered%20to%20support%20me%20financially%20once%20I%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F297672%2Fkashmir-couple-start-animal-rescue-shelters-for-wounded-animals%2F%5C%22%3Eexhaust%20my%20savings.%3C%2Fa%3E%20However%2C%20when%20I%20told%20my%20family%20that%20I%20planned%20to%20travel%20on%20foot%2C%20their%20reaction%20was%20exactly%20what%20I%20expected%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yati%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20planning%20on%20going%20to%20Kedarnath%20and%20my%20mother%20thought%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20become%20a%20%3Cem%3Esanyasi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(hermit)%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%20laughing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.c