20stop%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYati%20has%20also%20been%20documenting%20his%20journey%20on%20Instagram%20and%20has%20an%20earnest%20following%20of%2053%2C319%20thousand%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20have%20been%20loving%20our%20journey%20together%20and%20some%20brands%20have%20been%20generous%20enough%20to%20sponsor%20us.%20There%20is%20a%20UP-based%20gentleman%20who%20sponsored%20Buttercup%E2%80%99s%20food%20for%20the%20Chardham%20journey%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20childhood%20we%20have%20all%20heard%20our%20fathers%20and%20grandfathers%20brag%20and%20say%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eduniya%20dekhi%20hai%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fem%3E(I%20have%20seen%20the%20world)%2C%20well%2C%20with%20such%20diversity%20in%20India%2C%20they%20might%20have%20just%20peeked%20through%20the%20keyhole%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20door.%20However%2C%20not%20for%20Yati%2C%20as%20he%20and%20Buttercup%20have%20literally%20been%20seeing%20the%20world%2C%20one%20town%20at%20a%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693404383000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2Fyati-1693402264.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D328577%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Interested%20in%20slow%20travel%20and%20cultures%20across%20India%2C%20Yati%20Gaur%20decided%20to%20walk%20through%20the%20country.%20He%20has%20completed%20five%20walking%20expeditions%20covering%20states%20such%20as%20Goa%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20with%20his%20rescue%20dog%2C%20Buttercup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A37%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328577%2Fyati-gaur-from-uttar-pradesh-explores-india-on-foot-with-rescue-dog-travel-plans%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Nature-Based%20Solutions%20That%20Are%20Making%20Low-Income%20Communities%20Resilient%20to%20Climate%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDr%20Pramila%20Sanjaya%20has%20lived%20in%20Jaipur%20for%20over%2060%20years.%20Through%20this%20time%2C%20she%20has%20watched%20the%20city%20grow%20and%20expand%20over%20existing%20villages.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20used%20to%20be%20farms%20have%20now%20been%20converted%20into%20colonies%20and%20taken%20over%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291949%2Fmumbai-urban-gardener-grows-passion-fruits-and-beekeeps-on-terrace-garden-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultistory%20buildings%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20have%20also%20witnessed%20is%20the%20growth%20of%20informal%20settlements%20and%20slums%20across%20the%20city%2C%20which%20did%20not%20exist%20during%20my%20childhood.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrateek%20Tiwari%2C%20another%20Jaipur%20resident%20and%20CEO%20of%C2%A0%20Living%20Greens%20Organics%20Pvt.%20Ltd%2C%20also%20recalls%20a%20time%20when%20the%20city%20centre%20was%20full%20of%20trees.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%E2%80%99d%20visit%20my%20grandparents%20in%20Jaipur%20during%20May%2C%20summers%20weren%E2%80%99t%20something%20we%20would%20dread.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%E2%80%99d%20stay%20indoors%20between%2011%20am%20and%203%20pm%20%E2%80%94%20when%20it%20was%20very%20hot%20%E2%80%94%20but%20by%20the%20evening%2C%20the%20temperature%20would%20drop%20and%20it%20would%20be%20pleasantly%20cool%2C%20enough%20for%20us%20to%20sleep%20on%20the%20terrace%20at%20night.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20no%20longer%20have%20those%20spaces%20that%20helped%20keep%20the%20city%20cool.%20Jaipur%20has%20changed%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20for%20the%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20opines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaipur%20is%20only%20one%20among%20the%20several%20Indian%20citi